title: Game of Thrones
summary: Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.

title: Breaking Bad
summary: A high school chemistry teacher diagnosed with inoperable lung cancer turns to manufacturing and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's future.

title: Stranger Things
summary: When a young boy disappears, his mother, a police chief and his friends must confront terrifying supernatural forces in order to get him back.

title: Vikings
summary: Vikings transports us to the brutal and mysterious world of Ragnar Lothbrok, a Viking warrior and farmer who yearns to explore - and raid - the distant shores across the ocean.

title: Peaky Blinders
summary: A gangster family epic set in 1900s England, centering on a gang who sew razor blades in the peaks of their caps, and their fierce boss Tommy Shelby.

title: Friends
summary: Follows the personal and professional lives of six twenty to thirty-something-year-old friends living in Manhattan.

title: Black Mirror
summary: An anthology series exploring a twisted, high-tech multiverse where humanity's greatest innovations and darkest instincts collide.

title: Chernobyl
summary: In April 1986, an explosion at the Chernobyl nuclear power plant in the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics becomes one of the world's worst man-made catastrophes.

title: Sherlock
summary: A modern update finds the famous sleuth and his doctor partner solving crime in 21st century London.

title: Westworld
summary: Set at the intersection of the near future and the reimagined past, explore a world in which every human appetite can be indulged without consequence.

title: The Walking Dead
summary: Sheriff Deputy Rick Grimes wakes up from a coma to learn the world is in ruins and must lead a group of survivors to stay alive.

title: The Mandalorian
summary: The travels of a lone bounty hunter in the outer reaches of the galaxy, far from the authority of the New Republic.

title: Money Heist
summary: An unusual group of robbers attempt to carry out the most perfect robbery in Spanish history - stealing 2.4 billion euros from the Royal Mint of Spain.
